name: The Frog Made of Jam 2
description:
Jam Frog is back! Even though nobody asked him to be. Eat flies, rescue injured frogs, and move right while avoiding enemies. Now with a brand new health bar feature! When it runs out you will be sent back to the last checkpoint!

WASD or Arrow keys to move.
Up or space to jump. Down or shift to crouch.
Also playable with mouse.

Sequel to The Frog Made of Jam.

For "Unnecessary Sequels" Jam.
